|en=
Render target allows you to render a scene to a buffer (texture) instead of default buffer. It can be used for post-processing.

*A render target will always be the same size as game resolution.

*Note that a render target can be both input and output of rendering. Do input and output at the same time may cause error and the engine dose not check that.
|zh=
渲染目标允许用户渲染场景到一个缓冲区（纹理）而非默认缓冲区。可用于后处理。

*渲染目标的尺寸总是与游戏分辨率相同。

*渲染目标既可以作为渲染输入也可以作为渲染输出。同时用作输入和输出可能导致错误，引擎并未对此进行检查。
